snippet.title: Angry Birds Seasons Wreck The Halls Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
It's the most wonderful time of the year, but the pigs are up to their usual tricks! Use your best puzzle skills on the Angry Birds holiday calendar -- 25 new festive levels featuring gingerbread cookies, bells, twinkling lights, and candy canes. On the last day you'll meet the big pig himself... It's going to be an egg-citing holiday season!
